seller.oneLinerTitle: Design your dream with Ninja designer
seller.description: Hi, My Self Aaditya, Me and My team are really passionate for the graphic designing. Graphic designing is not just a work for us but it's our LIFE. We are having more than 5 years of experience in this field so we totally know how any graphic is important for particular business. We are Expert in Designing, Illustrator, Photoshop, Banner designing, Logo Design, Business Card proposals and all other kind of graphic work. I am available exclusively on Fiverr! Let's connect through Fiverr and make your design dreams come true :)

reviews.comment:
For the price, seller did well. Seller was out multiple days for a holiday (which is totally understandable). However, the first round of logos didn't come close to the initial mockup I sent. I had to "adjust" the logo, and the second round wasn't even close either. Finally, on the third round, it was close enough to take final approval of the delivery. I'll just work on the logo in some creative tools to get it tweaked to where I want it. 

All in all, good price and a good exercise, with a lackluster logo as a result.

I eventually got what I wanted here, but I experienced a significant delay in my project which I was hoping to have completed before the holidays.  I felt like I was asking for a simple edit of an existing asset, but it took 4 requests to get this result.  In the mean time I was delivered close to 20 files with different iterations that I wasn't looking for - I actually thought that I didn't get what I wanted until I finally looked again one last time and found that one of the files is what I wanted.  I understand he was probably giving me lots of options for future flexibility but in this case it hindered the completion of my simple ask.

I have worked with many people on Fiverr, this time was the fastest and best of quality. I didn't expect this is so on point I didn't even know I wanted the finished product perfect almost like she read my mind

I had an amazing experience! I was needing a logo in a time crunch and the seller not only went above and beyond to deliver to the specifics I was requesting but also provided many options and communication with the seller was beyond great! I wish I could rate the seller higher for their prompt and professional business. I will definitely be ordering again if the need ever arises again and will also be recommending to friends and family or anyone in need of logo creation.

Really happy with the final outcome. I was not happy with the first three proposals and was initially going to leave a good review because they were good, but not what I wanted. Aditya I insisted on giving it another try and ended up creating a logo I really liked and I am super happy with it. Would recommend!
